  Spearphishing simulation\
    Generates highly targeted phishing content\
    based on Scout's OSINT findings.\
    Knows the engineer's name, role,\
    recent LinkedIn activity, conference talks.\
    Crafts credential harvester that\
    mirrors the real Okta SSO portal exactly.\
    Simulates the full phishing lifecycle\
    against the Docker lab target.\
\
